### Create an intersection
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "x-int-1"
}

### List intersections
GET http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections

### Set plan
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/plan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nsGreenMs": 5000,
  "nsYellowMs": 1000,
  "ewGreenMs": 5000,
  "ewYellowMs": 1000
}

### Resume
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/resume

### State
GET http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/state

### Pause
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/pause

### Manual change (allowed only when paused)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "direction": "NORTH_SOUTH",
  "state": "GREEN"
}

### History
GET http://localhost:8080/api/traffic/intersections/x-int-1/history
